/tools/youtube-video-summarize-tool

searches youtube with input string and filters
returns results with thumbnail, title, description, viewcount, date and link
each result has summarize button, clicking it sends title+description+video_transcription_from_YT to GEMINI for summary
Chat w/ gemini modal opens, the first message is the summary, and the user can chat with gemini about the video, the context is always the video title, description and trascription
